th=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>-finput-charset&#x3D;UTF-8<br>-fexec-charset&#x3D;GBK</p></blockquote>\n<p> 如图：<br><img src=\"/img/note/code03.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br> 我的问题经过这两步操作之后再重新编译一遍代码就能正常运行啦。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/img/note/code04.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"></p>\n","feature":null,"text":"在使用codeblocks进行编程的时候我发现控制台输出会出现中文乱码，就像这样...","permalink":"/post/codeblocks输出中文乱码解决办法","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":386,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"实用教程","slug":"实用教程","count":5,"path":"api/categories/实用教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Codeblocks","slug":"Codeblocks","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Codeblocks.json"},{"name":"Bug修复","slug":"Bug修复","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Bug修复.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"kiyose408","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"img/kiyose.png","link":"/","description":"强风吹拂~","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/kiyose408","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"https://stackoverflow.com/users/22586365/kiyose408","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_4492248","juejin":"https://juejin.cn/user/3941068096931262","customs":{"gitee":{"icon":"/svg/gitee.svg","link":"https://gitee.com/kiyose408"}}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"codeblocks快捷键合集","uid":"e43f80fd110a34cfffcfbd2096485cd5","slug":"Codeblocks快捷键合集","date":"2021-10-30T05:49:00.000Z","updated":"2024-05-21T19:00:20.875Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Codeblocks快捷键合集.json","keywords":null,"cover":"img/web.jpg","text":"CodeBlocks常用操作快捷键...","permalink":"/post/Codeblocks快捷键合集","pho